As you hesitated, the soldier snatched the gun out of your hand. He and his men moved in on you and began to beat you mercilessly, until your face was bleeding and your eyes had swollen shut.\n\nThey cheerfully carried you to a personnel truck while singing Rumburgian victory songs.
